<li>Mullan, Fitzhugh. "The Metrics of the Physician Brain Drain." <i>New England Journal of Medicine,</i> Volume 353:1810-1818 <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2005-10-27"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="10-27"><a href="/wiki/October_27" title="October 27">October 27</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2005" title="2005">2005</a></span> Number 17 <a href="http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/full/353/17/1810" class="external text" title="http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/full/353/17/1810" rel="nofollow">online version</a></li>
